## 🚀 Final Full Push & Known Issues

A complete push to `origin main` was executed after unblocking Git from SQLite file locks.

### ✅ Resolved Blocks
- **Git Staging**: Updated `.gitignore` to exclude `*.db-shm` and `*.db-wal`. This allows `git add .` to succeed even while the database is being accessed by a running application.

### ⚠️ Known Broken Items (Documented in Push)

| Item | Status | Description |
|------|--------|-------------|
| **Librarian Crash** | 🩹 Patched / Unverified | `main.py` had an `AttributeError` on `sqlite3.Row.get()` during barcode scanning. Patched in source, but needs a full restart/test. |
| **Sync State** | 🔴 Interrupted | The startup "Full Mirror" sync from Supabase was interrupted. Local data may be out of sync with authority. |
| **Concurrency** | 🟡 Beta | WAL mode implemented in `database.py` but has not undergone high-concurrency stress testing yet. |
| **Deletion Sync** | 🟡 Unverified | New tombstone logic for bidirectional deletion tracking is implemented but untested for edge-case collisions. |

